    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.03754.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">323 N 6.<ptr target="loc.03754_n1"/></name> 
                    <date when="1891-03-03"><hi rend="underline">Tuesday</hi></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>
                    <handShift rend="manuscript"/>
                    Dear Walt
                </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I have been long wanting (longing) to write, just such an article as <hi rend="underline">Horace L. Traubel's</hi><ptr target="n4267"/> 
                about you in Mch Lippincott<ptr target="loc.07874_n3"/>:
                It is sound and perfect as a star&#8212;the best brochure anent Whitman ever produced&#8212;
            </p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Yours</salute> 
                <signed>JMS.</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
